# AI Customer Support Agent

## Problem

Companies spend too much time answering repetitive customer questions.

## Goal

Build an AI agent that helps businesses automate customer support.

## Features

- FAQ search
- AI generated responses
- Document-based answers
- Human escalation
- Conversation tracking
- Analytics

## Tech Stack

- Python
- Streamlit
- LLM API
- Vector Database
- LangChain

## Architecture

User Query
↓
AI Agent
↓
Knowledge Base / FAQ Search
↓
LLM Response
↓
Customer

## AI Concepts Used

- Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG)
- AI Agents
- Prompt Engineering
- Human-in-the-loop Systems

## Metrics

- Response accuracy
- Resolution rate
- Cost per ticket
- User satisfaction

## Status

Planning
